Ranger Help for: rhelp
======================

SYNTAX:      rhelp [topic]
             rh [topic]
             ranhelp [topic]
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command accesses the Ranger guild help system. Type 'rhelp' or
'rh' followed by a topic to view help on that subject. Without a topic,
it displays a list of available help categories.

EXAMPLES:
  rhelp skills       - View help on Ranger skills
  rhelp archery      - View help on archery
  rhelp general      - View general guild overview

HELP CATEGORIES:
  general            - Guild overview
  skills             - Skill system overview
  advancement        - How to advance in the guild
  terrains           - Terrain system
  followers          - Animal companion system
  weapons            - Ranger weapons
  archery            - Ranged combat
  equipment          - Gear and armour
